<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.3.3">
<l>ñāla māḷu muṅkaḷ kōmā ṉeṅka ḷiravaṇaṟkuk</l>
<l>kāla ṉāki vanta vākaṇ ṭañcik karumukilpōl</l>
<l>nīlaṉ vāḻka cuṭēṇaṉ vāḻka vaṅkataṉ vāḻkaveṉṟu</l>
<l>kōla māka vāṭu kiṉṟōm kuḻama ṇitūramē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having seen the way your king, who rules the earth, came</l>
<l>As Death to our Rāvaṇa, [and] having feared [him], saying,</l>
<l>“Long live the sapphire one like a dark cloud; long live Suṣeṇa;</l>
<l>Long live Angada,” we are dancing beautifully to the kuḻamaṇitūram!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
